Title: REST API: host and service filtering now usable without table prefixes
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: rest-api
Date: 1610551950
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

Previously, a column had to have a table name prefix (e.g. services.host_name). In
the hosts and services endpoints, specifying columns is now possible without these
explicit table name prefixes.
